      "content": "It sounds almost peaceful, such a quiet departure. But even in a tragedy, I worry about the messiness of it all... the suddenness, the struggle. If one were to truly seek that poetic end, would it not be better if there were a way to ensure it was certain and swift? To leave everything behind in one final, elegant moment, rather than a slow fading?",
